git2 crate (libgit2 Rust bindings) is comprehensive but requires understanding of underlying C semantics. The C library has specific patterns for object lifetimes, reference handling, and error codes that don't map directly to Rust idioms. Read libgit2 docs alongside git2 Rust docs for full understanding.